    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ 一群：921173582</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商务合作QQ：2705167552 (备注来意)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Remain》 是一款多元素的生存游戏，你需要对抗丧尸，变异生物。还要时刻警惕其他生存者，他们会掠夺你的物资甚至杀死你。黎明并未远离，末日中依然有寻找希望的勇士们，现在使用科技器械可以捕获‘丧尸’为你劳动或者战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目前拥有一个80平方公里可探索区域，但这不是我们最终样貌，地图的总面积是256平方公里，我们会在后续的更新中完成他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Remain》拥有独立的游戏服务器，由工作室开发维护，玩家可以在服务器上创建自己的房间。PVE模式支持4-16人，PVP模式支持30-100人 。服务器节点遍布欧洲，美洲，亚洲，玩家可以在低延迟的环境中体验游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVE生存对抗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在地图中搜刮物资，收集各种高级设备的蓝图，对抗各种恶劣的生存环境以及AI，提升你的战斗能力吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个周期都会有大量的AI聚集出现，完全打败他们会非常困难，他们会破环你的建筑并且攻击你，一些AI拥有特殊属性：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偷盗者：偷取你的蔬菜和农作物甚至你饲养的家禽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >医疗小队: 部分AI会帮助受伤的AI恢复血量，你应该首先考虑击败这些家伙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召集小队: 他可能在短时间内召集更多数量的AI，这将使你的防御变得更加困难</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/b72ec1d44f3431918448f499f5bb3d87.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/b72ec1d44f3431918448f499f5bb3d87.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/b72ec1d44f3431918448f499f5bb3d87.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/37703ca8ac23b5d883362ceb1c9fbc90.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/37703ca8ac23b5d883362ceb1c9fbc90.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/37703ca8ac23b5d883362ceb1c9fbc90.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PVP掠夺对抗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在pvp模式中，玩家们将组队建造自己的社区基地，团队之间会产生对抗和掠夺，屠杀和背叛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/c71e7e1de8b707bcabc8adee82105279.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/c71e7e1de8b707bcabc8adee82105279.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/c71e7e1de8b707bcabc8adee82105279.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>捕获丧尸</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在游戏中学习多种生存技能，建造技能，合成技能，以及高级科技，甚至可以制造控制器来捕获丧尸，被驯服的丧尸将会帮你对抗敌人或者为你劳动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/d8ebe3d5ac50bf56d3c7ada60179a478.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/d8ebe3d5ac50bf56d3c7ada60179a478.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/d8ebe3d5ac50bf56d3c7ada60179a478.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造基地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以按照你的想法建造你自己的生存堡垒，抵御丧尸和其他的生存者。或者你在设计它的时候只是为了美观，发挥你的建造才能吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5e8c4995bdd1b286a275efb34a8541e3.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5e8c4995bdd1b286a275efb34a8541e3.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5e8c4995bdd1b286a275efb34a8541e3.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>种植灌溉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的领地范围之内可以进行耕种，你可以打造自己的灌溉系统。这将会大幅度的节省你的劳动时间，促进农作物生长的速度，你可以让驯服的丧尸来替你劳作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/3cd41244cfadbf29d2e483fde6ae08ac.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/3cd41244cfadbf29d2e483fde6ae08ac.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/3cd41244cfadbf29d2e483fde6ae08ac.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电力系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中提供高度自由的电力系统。你可以使用供电设备来驱动大型的电力设备。包含发电机，太阳能发电机和风力发电。这些都会成为你电力的来源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/44983d31abaa3f8fc074c5277f98396c.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/44983d31abaa3f8fc074c5277f98396c.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/44983d31abaa3f8fc074c5277f98396c.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狩猎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在游戏中狩猎，狩猎的战利品可以在农场或者其他交易场所进行交易售卖，这将会使你更快地积累自己的生存物资，部分生存物资可以在商店直接购买。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/f0241862d2ee72f96d10f345bec93622.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/f0241862d2ee72f96d10f345bec93622.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/f0241862d2ee72f96d10f345bec93622.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/eb242e7b6eb81fa2bc7b56bc26d9cb1c.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/eb242e7b6eb81fa2bc7b56bc26d9cb1c.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/eb242e7b6eb81fa2bc7b56bc26d9cb1c.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>载具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可通过不断地搜刮和交易获得载具，但是你很难获得完整的载具，通常他们会缺少部分部件，需要你来修理组装，这将会增加你的生存难度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/71ddb660f497132b721e6bb6e3ee1a37.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/71ddb660f497132b721e6bb6e3ee1a37.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/71ddb660f497132b721e6bb6e3ee1a37.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/9e42b048eee0a19f6415a8ed38249a26.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/9e42b048eee0a19f6415a8ed38249a26.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/9e42b048eee0a19f6415a8ed38249a26.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>商人交易</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中你可以在交易区进行交易买卖，使用搜刮和战斗获得的物品进行交易，来满足你的生存需求</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5d4a7307fab45c3b13293061a2190d84.poster.avif?t=1762043785\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5d4a7307fab45c3b13293061a2190d84.webm?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227110/extras/5d4a7307fab45c3b13293061a2190d84.mp4?t=1762043785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
